    "body": "## Purpose\nSUMMARY:\n* Refactoring fp8.py\n* Clean up `process_weights_after_loading` by removing branches for block vs non-block\n* make methods into helpers that can be called from online too\n\nFOLLOW UP:\n* update FlashInfer FP8 to be able to be called from fp8.py [there are no llama models that exist)\n* investigate failures of FlashInfer Fp8 Per-tensor (also does not work on main)\n* update the marlin reshuffle and flashinfer register scales to be more transparent\n\n## Test Plan\n\n```bash\nMODEL_BLOCK := \"Qwen/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B-Instruct-FP8\"\nMODEL_TENSOR := \"amd/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1-FP8-KV\"\nGPUS := \"2\"\n\n# TRTLLM block - sm100\n# TRTLLM tensor - sm100\n# CUTLASS block - sm90\n# CUTLASS tensor - sm90\n# DEEP_GEMM block - sm100 / sm90\n# TRITON block - sm90\n# TRITON tensor - sm90\n# MARLIN block - sm90\n# MARLIN tensor - sm90\n# AITER block - rocm\n# AITER tensor - rocm\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_cutlass_block:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_USE_FLASHINFER_MOE_FP8=1 VLLM_FLASHINFER_MOE_BACKEND=throughput chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_cutlass_tensor:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_USE_FLASHINFER_MOE_FP8=1 VLLM_FLASHINFER_MOE_BACKEND=throughput  chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_TENSOR}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm100\nlaunch_trtllm_block:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_USE_FLASHINFER_MOE_FP8=1 VLLM_FLASHINFER_MOE_BACKEND=latency chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm100\nlaunch_trtllm_tensor:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_USE_FLASHINFER_MOE_FP8=1 VLLM_FLASHINFER_MOE_BACKEND=latency  chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_TENSOR}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90 / sm100\nlaunch_deepgemm:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=1 VLLM_MOE_USE_DEEP_GEMM=1 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_marlin_block:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_TEST_FORCE_FP8_MARLIN=1 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_marlin_tensor:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_TEST_FORCE_FP8_MARLIN=1 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_TENSOR}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_triton_block:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_MOE_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# sm90\nlaunch_triton_tensor:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_MOE_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_TENSOR}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\n# mi300x\nlaunch_aiter_block:\n     VLLM_ROCM_USE_AITER=1 VLLM_ROCM_USE_AITER_MOE=1 vllm serve {{MODEL}} -tp {{GPUS}}\n\neval_block:\n\tlm_eval \\\n\t\t--model local-completions \\\n\t\t--tasks gsm8k \\\n\t\t--model_args \"model={{MODEL_BLOCK}},base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n\neval_tensor:\n\tlm_eval \\\n\t\t--model local-completions \\\n\t\t--tasks gsm8k \\\n\t\t--model_args \"model={{MODEL_BLOCK}},base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n```\n\n## Test Result\n\n- block\n```bash (qwen fp8)\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8779|±  |0.0090|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8886|±  |0.0087|\n```\n\n- tensor\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=amd/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1-FP8-KV,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6391|±  |0.0132|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6353|±  |0.0133|\n```\n\nVALIDATED:\n- [X] sm90 launch_cutlass_block\n- [ ] sm90 launch_cutlass_tensor (not currently supported on main - only for L4, no such fp8 models exist)\n- [x] sm90 launch_deepgemm\n- [x] sm90 launch_marlin_block\n- [x] sm90 launch_marlin_tensor\n- [x] sm90 launch_triton_block\n- [x] sm90 launch_triton_tensor\n- [x] sm100 launch_trtllm_block\n- [ ] sm100 launch_trtllm_tensor (not currently supported on main - only for L4, no such fp8 models exist)\n- [x] sm100 launch_deepgemm\n- [x] mi300x launch_aiter_block\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
